{"id":"51533","title":"武极天下","writer":"蚕茧里的牛","dateline":"1444940765","updatetime":"1444940765","isover":"1","filesize":"21297236","linecount":"154653","wordcount":"6940798","imgpath":"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/UTB85NnJv0nJXKJkSaiyq6AhwXXaG.jpg","hash":"wujitianxia","urlhash":"","sign":"","desc":"起点VIP2015.8.27完结\n总推荐：1075262\n简介：\n一个梦想进入武府圣地的普通少年，立志追求极致武学。\n然而面对竞争激烈的考核，又有世家子弟的借势压人，小小平凡少年如何立足？\n宗门传承严格保密，核心功法概不外传，在功法传承如此难得天衍大陆，即便进了武府和宗门，想学到顶级武学又谈何容易？\n来自神域的小小魔方，展开一个强者的世界。\n功法要学就学最顶尖。\n生活职业要选就选别人都不会的。\n热血的对决，天才的竞争，三尺枪芒，千里直驱，武道极致，独步天下！","hot":"9551","num":"1740000","cid":"297","suggcate":"玄幻奇幻","suggcids":"47,297,205","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"1477771472","clicknum":"521","isvip":"1","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"男","isqiniu":"1","list":"0,2mv,6e7,a64,dhz,gjf,jjc,mni,puq,sq6,vlw,z5w,11y0,15in,18v4,1clb,1g66,1jlc,1msi,1q5e,1ta9,1wt0,1zd8,22di,25il,2954,2ci5,2fm6,2j1n,2mm2,2pyb,2tao,2wt9,2zui,33a3,35qw,38oy,3bq1,3edx,3h5i,3jsf,3mhm,3p19,3rpo,3v1g,3ybv,41bw,44o3,47zh,4av9,4dow,4gi6,4jtd,4n3g,4qgu,4tif,4wzd,5052,53fk,5636,59ax,5cbq,5ffd,5i01,5kl8,5ne7,5pzv,5sv8,5wcu,5zgu,62d6,663r,69qt,6d1r,6g8o,6k0g,6na6,6qbl,6sy1,6wgq,6zix,738a,75zf,78ps,7blm,7eao,7gwn,7jmo,7mlm,7pbn,7spu,7vch,7yg3,81f6,84uy,87zp,8ar6,8dh9,8gax,8j8f,8lys,8oah,8qpy,8tk6,8w2h,8yj9,917s,94kp,97w8,9b1g,9dv5,9gd3,9jn3,9n2t,9p9v,9se6,9w48,9zge,a35m,a68u,a9fx,acf8,afzp,aj1k,alkx,aobm,arly,auat,axjo,b0yc,b3ts,b6xt,b9xn,bcrr,bg2t,bja0,bmra,bq68,btel,bwti,bzrh,c2ab,c4hx,c6uj,c9cp,cc23,cej5,ch8x,cjs3,cmhq,cop6,crrj,cutz,cxiv,d0aw,d3cs,d6b8,d9fa,dc87,dexv,dhm4,djxx,dmo1,dp8e,ds1e,dufi,dwtg,dz05,e1o7,e4yf,e7lw,e9mz,ebzq,eerz,ehf1,ek2x,elz6,eo06,eqc7,esqh,euob,ex9v,f048,f30s,f5z9,f8u8,fbos,fe8g,fg6f,fio4,flkz,fo31,fqqo,ftbg,fvtc,fye2,g0tv,g3bg,g5pn,g7so,gaqz,gcvo,gfbq,ghpn,gk53,gm4u,goac,gpu7,gsqr,gv06,gx8u,gzie,h22n,h4s2,h7lw,hawb,he3u,hh32,hjpj,hmfo,hp46,hrnl,htxv,hw4l,hyki,i1co,i491,i7bm,i9s4,ic1x,if7b,ihp4,ik2f,imy3,iph7,irua,iuz3,ixwq,j0oz,j3f1,j5n5,j8ee,jbgl,je2d,jhd8,jk5x,jn59,jpzq,jswx,jvzz,jz4n